item.title: download
item.description: cdsctl workflow artifact download Download artifacts of one Workflow Run Synopsis Download artifacts of one Workflow Run cdsctl workflow artifact download [ PROJECT-KEY WORKFLOW-NAME ] NUMBER [ARTIFACT-NAME] [flags] Options --cdn-url string overwrite cdn url (deprecated) --exclude string exclude files from download - could be a regex: *.log Options inherited from parent commands -c, --context string cdsctl context name -f, --file string set configuration file --insecure (SSL) This option explicitly allows curl to perform "insecure" SSL connections and transfers.
